{"tid":1560323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"應 承 各 位 義 士 我 地 會 出 到 土 共 亡 黨 為 止","createTime":"2019-09-11T07:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T07:30:45.000Z","uid":107699,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"50ab6184ca02420de69d5dc7f27f86a712d6e7c9","tid":1560323,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:00:47.000Z","msg":"我謹此宣誓 我會同所有義士共同抗爭到土共滅亡為止<br />\n<br />\n無論需要幾多年 我都會同大家齊上齊落 <br />\n<br />\n無論發生咩事 只要土共港共唔滅亡 香港都唔會有真正嘅民主、自由、同公義<br />\n<br />\n而且我地日後都需要有武裝 好好保護我地自己嘅野！<br />\n<br />\n所以我地一定要繼續抗爭落去！<br />\n<br />\n義士唔係 condom<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">應承我 大家一定要繼續撐落去 抗爭到底！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"b9ccfeb7c60e709e1f2f88c61404afac39052a3e","tid":1560323,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:01:01.000Z","msg":"612"},{"pid":"d32e4f77d5510f84cb31e0bfb7fb0c484f506b13","tid":1560323,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:01:12.000Z","msg":"721"},{"pid":"09ae5ff1e626b6bd144dc3d4d2f2a7142356a02d","tid":1560323,"uid":107699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:01:25.000Z","msg":"831"},{"pid":"b8f120599bc00feafd00c0f385ab570f3ef4a64a","tid":1560323,"uid":284732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"一定喇! 天滅中共!"},{"pid":"f407db41eb3e23fe1ef1eb0b8444ce302e6b550d","tid":1560323,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:02:13.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公投：<br />\nA 袋住先<br />\nB 拆黨鐵<br />\nC 拆民建聯<br />\n<br />\n我反對暴力，我一定係A</span></strong>"},{"pid":"2137d4df3f47bd0df5ff12dfcacb4ba23313ce57","tid":1560323,"uid":193233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T07:03:46.000Z","msg":"天滅中共!